# Test substrings
set sentence Hello World
eval nop {global:sentence|substring 000 005|assert equals string Hello}
eval nop {global:sentence|substring 006 011|assert equals string World}
eval nop {global:sentence|substring 000 011|assert equals string Hello World}
eval nop {global:sentence|substring 000 100|assert equals string Hello World}
eval nop {global:sentence|substring 006 100|assert equals string World}
eval nop {global:sentence|substring 100 200|assert equals string}

exit